snippet.title: Peppy Pups Walks and Runs Huggable Dog TPF Toys Unboxing Toy Review by TheToyReviewer
snippet.description:
Peppy Pups is the soft and cuddly friend your child has been looking for, without the responsibility or commitment of a regular puppy! This walking dog toy has pep and bounce in his step wherever your child decides to walk him, making him a lively, enthusiastic companion. Let your little one use the leash so he can walk-along in the park, on the sidewalk, or even in the house. With a fluffy white tail and a snuggly coat, Peppy Pup will be easy to love and cuddle, just like a real puppy. This little stuffed toy features a silly facial expression, and he can even perform tricks, like flips. Peppy Pup will be your child's best friend. 

Peppy Pups is the perfect cuddly companion for your little one; this walking dog toy will be their new best friend.
This silly, stuffed puppy is soft, easy to love, and can even perform tricks like flipping.
Peppy Pup has pep in his step anywhere your youngster decides to take him; a leash is included, so he can walk right along-side your child.
Whether around the house, the neighborhood, or even just in the backyard, your child can take him anywhere.
A great way to give your child the company of a loyal companion, without the commitment or responsibility!

snippet.title: MICKEY MOUSE CLUBHOUSE Playset Disney Junior Toys Unboxing Video by Toy Review TV
snippet.description:
Toy Review TV presents a family friendly video MICKEY MOUSE CLUBHOUSE PLAYSET Fisher Price Disney Junior TOYS Family Review Video with Minnie Mouse.
There's so much to do at Mickey Clubhouse! Insert the mystery disc into the Mousekedoer to magically reveal the Mystery Mouseketool. Use the tool to create your own adventure or solve problems just like on the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse show. Drop the poseable figures from the bed to the slide, or into the elevator cup. Take characters to the observation deck where they can look through the telescope. The clubhouse door, oven door and refrigerator open, and figures can be stored inside the fold-down ears. There's even a hot air balloon that the figures fit inside! 9 play pieces store inside the fold-up playset.

Also see more fun kids toys videos like play doh, Surprise Eggs & Kinder Surprise Eggs at ToyReviewTV: https://www.youtube.com/user/SWCCToyReviewTV
